leadership-approach|process_results_people_vision|narrowing_3|3|Before Vision is added|People can add range before Vision is brought in deliberately, but the pattern may still narrow if Vision is left until later. The likely miss is decisions that solve the immediate pressure but do not explain what the work is meant to lead towards, especially when Process and Results already feel convincing.|vision|active|leadership-approach::process_results_people_vision::narrowing_3
